{"data": [{"id": "4741563", "title": "GameStop: Is This Time Different?", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"GameStop store sign\" data-id=\"1303187579\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3975px\" height=\"2650px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Dennis Diatel Photography</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>\"This time is different\" could be the four most dangerous words in trading. Markets rarely change. However, I have noticed a different pattern of behaviour in GameStop (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GME\" title=\"GameStop Corp.\">GME</a></span>) as it is making a more sustained uptrend rather than the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741563-gamestop-is-this-time-different", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 22:38:17"}, {"id": "4741577", "title": "United Back To Flying The Friendly Skies", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial shot showing an aircraft shadow flying over an idyllic beach scene, Barbados\" data-id=\"1321504180\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5464px\" height=\"3640px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Abstract Aerial Art</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Shares of United Airlines Holdings (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UAL\" title=\"United Airlines Holdings, Inc.\">UAL</a></span>) have surged over 25% in the last month taking their YTD gain to an incredible 140%. Last week, the stock even briefly traded above $100 to new all-time highs. As shown in the chart</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741577-united-back-to-flying-the-friendly-skies", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 22:30:00"}, {"id": "4741574", "title": "DXY's Rise Amidst Trump's BRICS Warning And French Uncertainty", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money on the edge\" data-id=\"1445810122\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"986px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Zain Vawda</em></p> <p>The US Dollar kicked December off on the front foot as market participants digested comments from US President-elect Donald Trump. This is the second week that markets have taken their cue from Trump's comments to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741574-dxys-rise-amidst-trumps-brics-warning-and-french-uncertainty", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 22:17:00"}, {"id": "4741572", "title": "China's Export Tax Rebate Shock: The Aluminum Market Faces A New Reality", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"detail shot of extruded aluminum industry in a plant\" data-id=\"674830596\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">fanjianhua/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><a href=\"https://agmetalminer.com/2024/12/02/china-export-tax-price-of-aluminum/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><em>Original Post</em></a></p> <p><em>By Stuart Burns</em></p> <p>A much-reported but little-understood development in the aluminum market this month has the potential to significantly alter the supply chain landscape for aluminum semi-finished metals in the year ahead. Beyond that, it</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741572-china-export-tax-rebate-shock-aluminum-market-faces-new-reality", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 22:15:00"}, {"id": "4741565", "title": "Summit Therapeutics Stock Set To Soar By Mid-2025 On HARMONi Phase 3 Trial", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close-up view of Mount Everest\" data-id=\"1595721515\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">The Summit of Mount Everest</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Karin Dohmen/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Summit Therapeutics Inc.</b> (NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SMMT\" class=\"ticker-link\">SMMT</a>) reached an important milestone in October, <a href=\"https://www.smmttx.com/pressrelease/promising-anti-tumor-activity-and-safety-of-ivonescimab-in-combination-therapies-in-crc-tnbc-and-hnscc-featured-at-esmo-2024-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\">completing enrollment</a> of its Phase III <a href=\"https://clinicaltrials.gov/study/NCT06396065?term=HARMONi&amp;rank=1\" rel=\"nofollow\">HARMONi</a> trial. Importantly, this study received <a href=\"https://www.biospace.com/drug-development/summit-therapeutics-announces-completion-of-enrollment-in-its-phase-iii-harmoni-trial-in-2l-egfrm-nsclc\" rel=\"nofollow\">fast track</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741565-summit-therapeutics-stock-set-to-soar-mid-2025-harmoni-phase-3-trial", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 22:10:07"}, {"id": "4741557", "title": "Navitas Semiconductor: The Secret Ingredient To AI's Next Leap", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170889984/image_2170889984.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Digital abstract CPU. AI - Artificial Intelligence and machine learning concept\" data-id=\"2170889984\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170889984/image_2170889984.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170889984/image_2170889984.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170889984/image_2170889984.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170889984/image_2170889984.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170889984/image_2170889984.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170889984/image_2170889984.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170889984/image_2170889984.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170889984/image_2170889984.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Vertigo3d/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Last August, I initiated my <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4716960-navitas-semiconductor-hidden-gem-stock\">coverage</a> on Navitas Semiconductor (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVTS\" title=\"Navitas Semiconductor Corporation\">NVTS</a></span>) with a buy rating due to its leading technological position in the emerging GaN power semiconductor industry. While the stock is down 11% since my</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170889984/image_2170889984.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741557-navitas-semiconductor-stock-secret-ingredient-to-ai-next-leap", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 22:02:51"}, {"id": "4741555", "title": "Primerica: Future Dividend Growth Potential, As Earnings Outlook Positive", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184985261/image_184985261.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close up of Life Insurance Policy\" data-id=\"184985261\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4256px\" height=\"2832px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184985261/image_184985261.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184985261/image_184985261.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184985261/image_184985261.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184985261/image_184985261.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184985261/image_184985261.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184985261/image_184985261.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184985261/image_184985261.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184985261/image_184985261.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">courtneyk</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Portfolio Sector: Financials / Insurance</h2> <p>In today's article as I gear up for the first trading week of December, the next article in my ongoing series called <em>The Future Investor with Albert Anthony</em> covers the financials sector, and more</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184985261/image_184985261.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741555-primerica-stock-future-dividend-growth-potential-as-earnings-outlook-positive", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 21:56:36"}, {"id": "4741541", "title": "Wall Street Lunch: Intel's Top Exec To Retire", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Intel Silicon Processor Chip\" data-id=\"1484082303\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">FinkAvenue</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div></p> <p>Listen below or on the go on <a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/wall-street-breakfast/id1358381502\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apple Podcasts</a> and <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/05uLjJxkVgQsRk8LWLCLpx?si=r3_yJgxiQiivJwNQG8WNew&amp;nd=1\" rel=\"nofollow\">Spotify</a></p> <p><div class=\"pcast hidden-print\">\n  <div class=\"pcast__section-1\">\n    <img alt=\"\" class=\"pcast__top-img pcast__marketing\" src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2018/11/21/podcast_series_header.png\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pcast__section-2\"><iframe src=\"https://widget.spreaker.com/player?episode_id=63110181&amp;theme=light&amp;playlist=false&amp;playlist-continuous=false&amp;chapters-image=true&amp;episode_image_position=right&amp;hide-logo=true&amp;hide-likes=true&amp;hide-comments=true&amp;hide-sharing=true&amp;hide-download=true&amp;color=ff6900\" width=\"100%\" height=\"200px\" frameborder=\"0\" sap-id=\"4\"></iframe></div>\n  <div class=\"pcast__section-3\">\n    <div class=\"pcast__ad-container\"></div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</p> <p>David Zinsner and Michelle Johnston Holthaus <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4353857-intel-announces-ceo-gelsinger-retiring-replaced-with-co-ceos\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">will replace</a> Pat Gelsinger. (0:15) Morgan Stanley adjust ratings on <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4353662-okta-cloudflare-upgraded-at-morgan-stanley-sentinelone-tenable-downgraded\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">cybersecurity stocks</a>. (3:22) OpenAI looks <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4353580-openai-looks-to-add-advertising-to-artificial-intelligence-products-cfo-tells-ft\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">at ads</a>. (4:06)</p> <p>This is an abridged transcript of the podcast.</p> <p>Our top story so far. This morning, Intel (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INTC\" title=\"Intel Corporation\">INTC</a></span>) made the surprising announcement that CEO <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4353857-intel-announces-ceo-gelsinger-retiring-replaced-with-co-ceos\">Pat Gelsinger is retiring</a> and will be replaced by co-CEOs David Zinsner and Michelle Johnston Holthaus.</p> <p>Gelsinger is also stepping down from the company's board of directors. Both departures are effective December 1.</p> <p>Holthaus has been appointed to the newly created position of CEO of Intel Products, while Frank Yeary was named interim executive chair.</p> <p>Yeary said: \u201cWhile we have made significant progress in regaining manufacturing competitiveness and building the capabilities to be a world-class foundry, we know that we have much more work to do at the company and are committed to restoring investor confidence.\u201d</p> <p>In August, the company said that it was cutting staff by 15% and spending by $10 billion as it works to streamline its operations. Intel shares, which rose slightly after the announcement, are down 50% year to date.</p> <p>In today\u2019s trading, stocks are mixed with the Nasdaq (COMP.IND) outperforming, up nearly 1%.</p> <p>Goldman\u2019s trading desk says sentiment \u201creally is varied depending on where you look but it would appear we\u2019ve seen selling in prime and most sentiment indicators look quite restrained.\u201d</p> <p>\u201cThe US market is expensive ... very much so, but that in it of itself does not preclude further gains as we head into the end of the year.\"</p> <p>\"This week will really be all about jobs and ... the market will be hoping they are not too firm (GS +235k, consensus +200k) just enough to keep Fed from having an excuse to skip December.\"</p> <p>If you want great coverage going into that big Fed meeting, be sure to check out our Cyber Monday deal. That\u2019s 20% off all Seeking Alpha products. Our team covers financial news round the clock, and with our Listen to Article feature you can take your research on the go. Check out <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/\">SeekingAlpha.com</a>.</p> <p>On the economic front, the ISM Manufacturing index <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4354331-us-ism-manufacturing-beats-consensus-in-november\">improved to 48.4</a> in November from 46.5 in October, topping the 47.6 consensus.</p> <p>The manufacturing sector contracted for the eighth straight month, while the overall U.S. economy expanded for the 55th month.</p> <p>Pantheon Macro economist Oliver Allen notes the new orders index jumped to 50.4, an eight-month high, which \u201csuggests that the drop in corporate bond yields in recent quarters and a slight improvement in external demand are starting to support U.S. manufacturers.\u201d</p> <p>But the \u201cslight improvements from a low level still suggest that the manufacturing sector is far from out of the woods just yet.\u201d</p> <p>Among active stocks today, Marvell Technology (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MRVL\" title=\"Marvell Technology, Inc.\">MRVL</a>), which reports earnings later this week, rose as the firm<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4353989-marvell-technology-stock-up-as-it-expands-collaboration-with-amazon-web-services\"> expanded its strategic collaboration with Amazon Web Services</a>. Marvell expanded the collaboration for electronic design automation in the cloud to deliver its silicon solutions.</p> <p>Citi downgraded Nu Holdings (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NU\" title=\"Nu Holdings Ltd.\">NU</a>), which operates NuBank in Brazil and Mexico, to Sell from Neutral as it faces a <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4353771-nu-holdings-cut-to-sell-at-citi\">tougher road for growth after rapid expansion</a>.</p> <p>Analyst Gustavo Schroden said it will take longer than expected for alternative revenue sources, such as payroll loans in Brazil, Mexico, and Colombia, to offset the slowdown in credit cards and personal loans in Brazil.</p> <p>And Morgan Stanley made several <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4353662-okta-cloudflare-upgraded-at-morgan-stanley-sentinelone-tenable-downgraded\">ratings changes</a> to cybersecurity, upgrading Okta (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OKTA\" title=\"Okta, Inc.\">OKTA</a>) and Cloudflare (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NET\" title=\"Cloudflare, Inc.\">NET</a>) and downgrading SentinelOne (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/S\" title=\"SentinelOne, Inc.\">S</a>) and Tenable (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TENB\" title=\"Tenable Holdings, Inc.\">TENB</a>).</p> <p>Okta was raised to Overweight from Equal Weight. Analysts said they see the demand environment \"stabilizing,\" the headwinds from competition appear to be easing, and new products are taking hold. They boosted Cloudflare to Overweight from Equal Weight, saying there is a path to \"sustainable\" 25% to 30% revenue growth over the next few years.</p> <p>SentinelOne was cut to Equal Weight from Overweight on \"slower expected demand\" for the core endpoint security market in 2025, along with a challenging competitive and pricing environment. Tenable was also cut to Equal Weight from Overweight on pricing pressures in the vulnerability management market.</p> <p>In other news of note, Microsoft-backed (M<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/S\" title=\"SentinelOne, Inc.\">S</a>FT) OpenAI is discussing plans to <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4353580-openai-looks-to-add-advertising-to-artificial-intelligence-products-cfo-tells-ft\">introduce advertising</a> to its range of products, as the ChatGPT maker seeks new revenue sources.</p> <p>The Financial Times says the group has been hiring ad talent from big tech rivals such as Meta (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/META\" title=\"Meta Platforms, Inc.\">META</a>) and Google (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GOOGL\" title=\"Alphabet Inc.\">GOOGL</a>).</p> <p>In a statement, OpenAI CFO Sarah Friar said, \"Our current business is experiencing rapid growth and we see significant opportunities within our existing business model. While we\u2019re open to exploring other revenue streams in the future, we have no active plans to pursue advertising.\u201d</p> <p>And in the Wall Street Research Corner, Fitch/BMI <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4353388-commodity-roundup-energy-prices-base-metals-to-be-under-pressure-in-2025-bmi-says\">expects commodity prices to be under pressure in 2025</a>, driven by abundant supply and U.S. dollar strength.</p> <p>In energy, prices continue to see downside pressures as soft demand and resilient supplies outweigh the premium of geopolitical risk.</p> <p>BMI lowered its 2025 Brent forecast to an average of $76 a barrel, a 5% decline from 2024\u2019s annual average of $80. But the front-month Henry Hub gas benchmark is expected to gain 42% in 2025, rising to $3.40 per million BTUs.</p> <p>\"The developing La Ni\u00f1a conditions are expected to fuel a colder than normal Northern Hemisphere winter, which should support natural gas prices both in the U.S. and abroad,\" BMI said.</p> <p>Analysts expect significant volatility in metals on the back of anticipated U.S. dollar strength and Trump-led trade policy shifts, with sentiment highly sensitive towards a long-awaited Mainland Chinese demand turnaround. Gold is expected to average $2,500 per ounce.</p> <div class=\"before_last_paragraph-piano-placeholder\"></div><p>Agricultural commodities are expected to ease but remain historically elevated.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741541-wall-street-lunch-intels-top-exec-to-retire", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 21:51:00"}, {"id": "4741550", "title": "Gambling.com Group: Unlocking Value In Online Gambling