its growth rates are somewhat pedestrian.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150394012/image_2150394012.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741550-gamblingcom-group-unlocking-value-in-online-gambling", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 21:38:46"}, {"id": "4741547", "title": "Philip Morris Continues To Reward Shareholders", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92172352/image_92172352.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"An up close view of a package of several cigarettes\" data-id=\"92172352\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5616px\" height=\"3744px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92172352/image_92172352.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92172352/image_92172352.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92172352/image_92172352.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92172352/image_92172352.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92172352/image_92172352.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92172352/image_92172352.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92172352/image_92172352.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92172352/image_92172352.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">mariusFM77</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Philip Morris International Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PM\" title=\"Philip Morris International Inc.\">PM</a></span>) is a multinational tobacco company with a $200 billion market cap. That makes the company the largest publicly traded tobacco company in the world, with a dividend yield of more than 4%. As we'll see throughout</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92172352/image_92172352.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741547-philip-morris-continues-to-reward-shareholders", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 21:27:25"}]}